3. useCreateSession - Mutation for creating new session
4. useUpdateSession - Mutation for updating session (title/status)
5. useDeleteSession - Mutation for deleting session
6. useSessionMessages(session_id) - Fetch message history
7. useSessionStats(session_id) - Fetch session statistics

